Cavalcade O' Card Games!  Includes 5 games;
Crazy 8's, BlackJack, a matching game,  
52-Pickup, and Klondike solitaire.
Environment options include a dozen card 
backs and classical music scores.  Register 
to obtain 4 more games including three 
solitaires. Online instructions. Mouse 
required.  Requires at least a 286 and VGA.

